Title: Milwaukee M12 hydraulic presstool Mset
Description: Compact and light, weighing just 1.8kg, the Milwaukee M12 sub compact force logic hydraulic press tool combines powerful results with user comfort. Offering seamless battery-to-tool communication, which prevents incomplete pressing using a pre-press battery check, this smart tool minimises wasted time and frustration while ensuring long-term reliability, providing a proven 40,000+ cycles between calibration inspections. This tool is fitted with a RedLithium battery pack for fade-free performance for longer runtime and an improved tool lifespan.
